headline: Invitation Homes' Q4 FFO Meets Estimates, Revenues Top, Rents Rise Y/Y
summary: INVH's Q4 FFO comes in line with estimates, and revenues beat as same-store NOI climbs despite lower occupancy. The company rolls out its 2026 core FFO outlook.
